@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eqgybs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.74
    v2 = ((tmp - (tmp + 0.09 + v1 + 0.61)) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.65) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.59)))
    v2 = v2
    v1 = (v2 - ((v0 + 0.64 + tmp + 0.16) / (tmp + 0.86 / tmp + 0.14)))
    v2 = 0.38
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.05) * wp.abs((v0 + 0.69 * v1 + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
